<chapter line="1">Vatthuvisodhanīgāthā</chapter>
<hangnum line="2" number="4"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="3"> Buddhoti ko buddhaguṇo ti ko so,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="4">Acintayādittamupāgato yo;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="5">Anaññasādhāraṇabhūtamatthaṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="6">Akāsi kiṃ so kimavoca buddho.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="7" number="5"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="8"> Visuddhakhandhasantāno buddhoti niyamo kato,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="9">Khandhasantānasuddhī tu guṇoti niyamo kato.</gathalast>
<hangnum line="10" number="6"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="11"> Akāsi kiccāni dinesu pañca,</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="12">Pasādayañciddhibalena sena;</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="13">Janānasesaṃ cariyānukūlaṃ,</gatha3>
<gathalast line="14">Ñatvānavocānusayappahānaṃ.</gathalast>
